[32m+[m[32m# Power Infrastructure Architecture[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Purpose[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mPower Infrastructure is an engineering platform for managing IBM Power environments.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe project combines inventory, validation, documentation, reporting, and automation into a repeatable engineering framework.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mRather than building isolated automation scripts, Power Infrastructure provides reusable capabilities that support the complete operational lifecycle.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# Architectural Goals[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe architecture is designed to:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- establish authoritative infrastructure inventory[m
[32m+[m[32m- standardize operational validation[m
[32m+[m[32m- generate documentation automatically[m
[32m+[m[32m- provide reusable engineering workflows[m
[32m+[m[32m- minimize manual operational effort[m
[32m+[m[32m- improve operational consistency[m
[32m+[m[32m- support enterprise change management[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# Core Engineering Capabilities[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe project is organized around a small number of core capabilities.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Inventory[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mInventory discovers and maintains information about the environment from authoritative sources.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mExamples include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- IBM HMC[m
[32m+[m[32m- AIX[m
[32m+[m[32m- VIOS[m
[32m+[m[32m- Pure Storage[m
[32m+[m[32m- Veeam[m
[32m+[m[32m- project metadata[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mInventory answers:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m> What exists?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Operational Reviews[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mOperational Reviews evaluate the current operational state of infrastructure.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mReviews are read-only.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mExamples include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- MQ[m
[32m+[m[32m- filesystem[m
[32m+[m[32m- AIX[m
[32m+[m[32m- HMC[m
[32m+[m[32m- VIOS[m
[32m+[m[32m- Pure Storage[m
[32m+[m[32m- backup[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mOperational Reviews answer:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m> What is the current state?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Workflow Engine[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe Workflow Engine performs validated operational changes.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mExamples include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- user provisioning[m
[32m+[m[32m- user removal[m
[32m+[m[32m- disaster recovery[m
[32m+[m[32m- patching[m
[32m+[m[32m- LPAR deployment[m
[32m+[m[32m- LPAR decommissioning[m
[32m+[m[32m- backup restoration[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe Workflow Engine answers:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m> How can the environment be changed safely?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Documentation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDocumentation is generated whenever practical.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mExamples include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- environment summaries[m
[32m+[m[32m- inventory reports[m
[32m+[m[32m- disaster recovery documentation[m
[32m+[m[32m- operational review reports[m
[32m+[m[32m- change documentation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDocumentation answers:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m> How do we preserve engineering knowledge?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Reporting[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mReporting communicates engineering information.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mExamples include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- capacity reports[m
[32m+[m[32m- monthly operational reports[m
[32m+[m[32m- health summaries[m
[32m+[m[32m- trend analysis[m
[32m+[m[32m- executive summaries[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mReporting answers:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m> What information should engineers and management receive?[m
[32m+[m
