[32m+[m[32m## Operational Health Framework[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe Operational Health framework continued to mature into a reusable operational review platform built on the standard Workflow Engine.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mRather than creating standalone diagnostic scripts, Operational Health workflows follow the common execution lifecycle:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```text[m
[32m+[m[32mPrepare[m
[32m+[m[32m↓[m
[32m+[m[32mValidate[m
[32m+[m[32m↓[m
[32m+[m[32mCollect[m
[32m+[m[32m↓[m
[32m+[m[32mEvaluate[m
[32m+[m[32m↓[m
[32m+[m[32mQuick View[m
[32m+[m[32m↓[m
[32m+[m[32mReport[m
[32m+[m[32m↓[m
[32m+[m[32mStructured Results[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mRecent enhancements include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m* Modular evidence collection roles[m
[32m+[m[32m* Modular evaluation roles[m
[32m+[m[32m* Host-specific artifact workspaces[m
[32m+[m[32m* Fleet operational review support[m
[32m+[m[32m* Fleet summary generation[m
[32m+[m[32m* Standardized Markdown reports[m
[32m+[m[32m* Standardized JSON results[m
[32m+[m[32m* Generic quick-view summaries[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mCurrent AIX operational review coverage includes:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m* Operating system validation[m
[32m+[m[32m* NTP validation[m
[32m+[m[32m* Paging space utilization[m
[32m+[m[32m* Memory utilization summary[m
[32m+[m[32m* CPU utilization summary[m
[32m+[m[32m* Network validation[m
[32m+[m[32m* Bootlist validation[m
[32m+[m[32m* Boot device validation[m
[32m+[m[32m* Dump device validation[m
[32m+[m[32m* Disk path validation[m
[32m+[m[32m* Filesystem capacity[m
[32m+[m[32m* AIX error report analysis[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mReference implementations currently include:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m* MQ Operational Health[m
[32m+[m[32m* AIX Operational Health[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe framework now supports both single-host operational reviews and inventory group reviews using the same workflow architecture. Each reviewed host generates independent artifacts which can then be aggregated into fleet-level operational summaries.[m
